            <div class="all-codes-grid">
              <div class="code-item"><span class="code-num">2395</span><span>水泥、石膏及混凝土制品制造</span></div>
              <div class="code-item"><span class="code-num">2592</span><span>金属机械加工；金属表面处理及热处理</span></div>
