              <div class="code-item"><span class="code-num">3313</span><span>电子和光学设备维修</span></div>
              <div class="code-item"><span class="code-num">3314</span><span>电气设备维修</span></div>
              <div class="code-item"><span class="code-num">3315</span><span>运输设备维修和保养</span></div>
